}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "250-541800-202" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The power adapter shown in the FCC photos is an '''Aztech''' branded SWM11-12120 (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 0.4A -> 12VDC, 1.0A).
